Grading: This course is graded on the Undergraduate Regular scale.

ENGH 344: Development of the American Novel since 1914. 3 credits.
Works by Fitzgerald, Hemingway, Faulkner, Dos Passos, Wolfe, Bellow, and Nabokov. Offered by English. Limited to three attempts.
