ENGH 722: Composition Pedagogies and Programs in Context. 3 credits.
Examines scholarship on pedagogy, curriculum design and assessment, faculty development, and program management related to the practice of teaching or training writers in an institutional setting: two- and four-year colleges, K-12 schools, and workplace training seminars. Offered by English. May not be repeated for credit.
